Program: Great Lives
Title: CLR James
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0076b7s
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 24 Oct 2014
Darcus Howe chooses activist and philosopher CLR James, with help from his biographer Farrukh Dhondy. Presented by Humphrey Carpenter. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? From 2002. Show less